---
import Card from "./Card/index.astro";
---

<Card colSpan="md:col-span-1" rowSpan="md:row-span-6" title="About me">
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
    <div class="text-sm font-light">
      <p>
        Hi, I'm Tim, a high school developer from Germany.
        I'm a student working on personal projects to enhance my software development skills.
        <br />
        My primary tools of choice include: 
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
        <li>Python</li>
        <li>GitHub</li>
        <li>Swift</li>
        <li>Vercel</li>
        <li>Google Antigravity</li>
        <li>Postman</li>
        <li>Supabase</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <p class="text-sm font-light">
      Beyond coding, I'm passionate about design, 3D modelling, 3D printing and traveling.
      A few hobbys of mine are biking and making music, they're
      some really important pieces to me.
    </p>
    <p class="text-sm font-light">
      My goal is to continually expand my knowledge and grow within the field of computer science.
    </p>
  </div>
</Card>
